##两表join的情况下，何时可以下降相关条件
EXPLAIN select /*+leading(t1 t2) use_nl(t1 t2)*/ t1.a, t2.a from tt t1 inner join t_r4_01_20 t2 on t1.a = t2.b order by t1.a desc, t2.a desc;
Query Plan
=================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                         |NAME       |EST. ROWS|COST|
-----------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN MERGE SORT DISTR     |           |40       |1600|
|1 | EXCHANGE OUT DISTR              |           |40       |1600|
|2 |  SORT                           |           |40       |1600|
|3 |   NESTED-LOOP JOIN              |           |40       |1560|
|4 |    EXCHANGE IN DISTR            |           |40       |45  |
|5 |     EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (BC2HOST)|           |40       |44  |
|6 |      GRANULE ITERATOR           |           |40       |44  |
